```json
{
  "translations": [
    {
      "block_id": "p13_b1",
      "translation": "AIA is a trusted partner for customers, providing peace of mind as they focus on financial security and family protection. Despite the significant impact of the COVID-19 pandemic,"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p13_b2",
      "translation": "I sincerely thank our employees, agents, and partners for adapting to new ways of working and ensuring uninterrupted support to our customers"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p13_b3",
      "translation": "while demonstrating flexibility and dedication to their responsibilities."
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p13_b4",
      "translation": "Overview\nFinancial and Operational Review\nCorporate Governance\nOther Information\nFinancial Statements"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p13_b5",
      "translation": "Since the pandemic began, our business teams have responded swiftly and actively helped mitigate its impact on communities while ensuring employee safety. The Group"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p13_b6",
      "translation": "has implemented comprehensive measures, including financial support, medical supplies, complimentary coverage, healthcare access, streamlined processes, and"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p13_b7",
      "translation": "accelerated claims payments, which I am proud of. We continue to find every reason to pay claims, having paid over USD 16 billion in insurance benefits and claims"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p13_b8",
      "translation": "during the year, providing essential financial protection to our customers."
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p13_b9",
      "translation": "Although measures to contain COVID-19 reduced new business value to USD 2.765 billion, sales momentum turned positive as restrictions eased, with strong momentum"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p13_b10",
      "translation": "in early 2021, showing 15% year-on-year growth in new business value in the first two months. Our large and growing portfolio of in-force policies provides"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p13_b11",
      "translation": "high-quality recurring income, driving a 5% increase in after-tax operating profit in 2020, with basic free surplus growing 7%."
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p13_b12",
      "translation": "As of December 31, 2020, embedded value equity reached a record USD 67.2 billion, with Group local capital adequacy ratio at 374%, demonstrating"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p13_b13",
      "translation": "our strong capital position and prudent financial management."
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p13_b14",
      "translation": "The Board recommends a 7.5% increase in the 2020 final dividend to HKD 1.0030 per share. This reflects AIA's long-standing prudent, sustainable, and progressive dividend"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p13_b15",
      "translation": "policy, enabling us to capture future growth opportunities while maintaining financial flexibility."
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p13_b16",
      "translation": "AIA possesses significant competitive advantages that distinguish us in a competitive market. With decades of operations in Asia, we have an unparalleled"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p13_b17",
      "translation": "platform and hold leading positions in most of our markets. Our consistent 100% focus on Asia helps us capture growth opportunities across the world's"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p13_b18",
      "translation": "most attractive life insurance region. This focus, combined with our leadership's extensive Asia experience and our talented workforce,"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p13_b19",
      "translation": "has been key to our strong performance."
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p13_b20",
      "translation": "Our unparalleled distribution strength provides direct customer access and high-quality professional advice, helping meet Asia's growing long-term protection"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p13_b21",
      "translation": "and savings needs. Today, customers increasingly expect companies to address their needs sustainably. AIA has a market-leading brand"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p13_b22",
      "translation": "built on helping people live healthier, longer, better lives."
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p13_b23",
      "translation": "We aim to lead globally in technology application, enhancing connectivity, scale, and efficiency. Deeper data analytics insights help"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p13_b24",
      "translation": "us create unique, personalized customer experiences. Products and services tailored to individual needs and lifestyles have transformed how people view life insurance,"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p13_b25",
      "translation": "establishing a strong foundation for long-term customer relationships."
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p13_b26",
      "translation": "Although 2020 was unprecedented, I am more optimistic than ever about Asia's life insurance outlook and AIA's future. We continue to challenge ourselves,"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p13_b27",
      "translation": "developing our priorities to ensure we meet evolving customer expectations and financial needs. Our new corporate strategy builds on AIA's existing strengths,"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p13_b28",
      "translation": "driving transformation to deliver the best service to customers in the future."
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p13_b29",
      "translation": "2020 Annual Report\n011"
    }
  ]
}
```
